name: blocked
title: Blocked user ?
help: Specify whether to block the user for an indeterminate times.
help_t: 指定是否限定用户只在一段时间内有效。

name: activeFrom
title: Active user from
help: Specify whether to allow the user from this specific date.
help_t: 指定是否允许用户在该时间之后有效。

name: activeTo
title: Active user to
help: Specify whether to allow the user until this specific date.
help_t: 指定是否允许用户在该时间之前有效。
